# Harness file edits

Changes under `.claude/`, `.codex/`, `.cursor/`, or `process/development-protocols/` affect the agent harness.

When modifying these paths:

- Keep Claude (`.claude/agents/`), Codex (`.codex/agents/`), and Cursor (`.cursor/agents/`) agent surfaces in parity.
- Run `node .claude/skills/vc-audit-vc/scripts/validate-agent-parity.mjs` and Cursor validators after agent changes.
- Regenerate Cursor agents with `node .claude/skills/vc-audit-vc/scripts/generate-cursor-agents.mjs --write` when Claude agent bodies change.
- Prefer durable updates in `process/context/` over hardcoding project facts in root instruction files.
